{"tid":2407011,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"前變態上司Add IG","createTime":"2021-02-13T16:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T02:20:28.000Z","uid":66271,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e322cf58d4fb0a06e2dad1bc833783d7105247","tid":2407011,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T16:06:22.000Z","msg":"社交媒體是每個人的「秘密花園」，有人選擇公諸同好，也有人選擇只與摰友分享。而在職場上，不少人都抗拒加同事的Social Media，因為不是每個人都樂意與同事分享私人生活，更莫論是上司了！<br />\n<br />\n最近有打工仔在網上分享前變態上司Add Social Media的經歷，而他毫不猶豫立即Decline，更霸氣道︰「Bye Bye啦！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://res01.ctgoodjobs.hk/images/resources/news/content/H/Image_20210210020258_77572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres01.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Fimages%2Fresources%2Fnews%2Fcontent%2FH%2FImage_20210210020258_77572.jpg&h=2193b360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://res01.ctgoodjobs.hk/images/resources/news/content/H/Image_20210210020258_77573.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres01.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Fimages%2Fresources%2Fnews%2Fcontent%2FH%2FImage_20210210020258_77573.jpg&h=ed39b3fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://res01.ctgoodjobs.hk/images/resources/news/content/H/Image_20210210020258_77574.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres01.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Fimages%2Fresources%2Fnews%2Fcontent%2FH%2FImage_20210210020258_77574.jpg&h=e7fcbae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://res01.ctgoodjobs.hk/images/resources/news/content/H/Image_20210210020258_77575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres01.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Fimages%2Fresources%2Fnews%2Fcontent%2FH%2FImage_20210210020258_77575.jpg&h=2b56ba79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://res01.ctgoodjobs.hk/images/resources/news/content/H/Image_20210210020258_77576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fres01.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Fimages%2Fresources%2Fnews%2Fcontent%2FH%